# Phase 3.6A: Legacy Code Cleanup & Deletion Plan

This plan outlines Phase 3.6A, focusing solely on the cleanup and deletion of legacy Express routes, controllers, and services that are no longer serving live traffic or imported by active system nodes. 

All proxy model wrappers in `src/models/` remain active and untouched in this phase.

---

## 1. Deletion Matrix

The following matrix lists every candidate file proposed for deletion in Phase 3.6A, detailing its path, referencing files, and evidence proving it can be safely removed.

| File Path | Category | Referencing Files | Deletion Evidence & Justification |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `src/routes/auth.js` | Route | None | **0 active references**. This was a route compatibility wrapper not imported or registered by the consolidated Express router in `index.js`. |
| `src/routes/booking.js` | Route | None | **0 active references**. Express routes are fully Swapped to clean `bookingRoutes.js` in `index.js`. |
| `src/routes/payment.js` | Route | None | **0 active references**. Express routes are fully Swapped to clean `paymentRoutes.js` in `index.js`. |
| `src/routes/review.js` | Route | None | **0 active references**. Express routes are fully Swapped to clean `reviewRoutes.js` in `index.js`. |
| `src/routes/worker.js` | Route | None | **0 active references**. Express routes are fully Swapped to clean `workerRoutes.js` in `index.js`. |
| `src/controllers/authController.js` | Controller | None | **0 active references**. All incoming auth requests are handled by clean `AuthController.js`. |
| `src/controllers/bookingController.js` | Controller | None | **0 active references**. All incoming booking requests are handled by clean `BookingController.js`. |
| `src/controllers/chatController.js` | Controller | None | **0 active references**. All incoming chat requests are handled by clean `ChatController.js`. |
| `src/controllers/paymentController.js` | Controller | None | **0 active references**. All incoming payment requests are handled by clean `PaymentController.js`. |
| `src/controllers/review.js` | Controller | None | **0 active references**. All incoming review requests are handled by clean `ReviewController.js`. |
| `src/controllers/workerController.js` | Controller | None | **0 active references**. The final reference `/admin/overview` was migrated in Phase 3.5.1 to clean `WorkerController.js`. |
| `src/services/authService.js` | Service | None | **0 active references**. Only imported by legacy `authController.js`. Not used by active code. |
| `src/services/locationService.js` | Service | None | **0 active references**. Only imported by legacy `workerController.js`. Not used by active code. |

